WEBVTT

03:25.940 --> 03:26.874
<i>Reo.</i>

03:36.718 --> 03:38.251
You scared me.

03:38.619 --> 03:40.555
<i>Did you get what I asked for?</i>

03:40.955 --> 03:41.889
Yeah.

03:45.727 --> 03:46.661
Hey, Dad.

03:48.196 --> 03:49.530
I'm gonna beat you.

03:49.931 --> 03:51.431
I'm gonna beat you at this game.

03:51.632 --> 03:52.934
<i>All right. We'll see.</i>

04:22.029 --> 04:24.198
<i>The number</i>
<i>of homicides and suicides</i>

04:24.431 --> 04:26.601
<i>continues to climb</i>
<i>since the release</i>

04:26.801 --> 04:29.369
<i>of the groundbreaking footage</i>
<i>of Reo Nakata</i>

04:29.704 --> 04:31.939
<i>playing cards</i>
<i>with his dead father.</i>

04:32.339 --> 04:35.176
<i>Dr. Stevensen</i>
<i>of the Life Beyond Institute</i>

04:35.375 --> 04:37.812
<i>is live now to address</i>
<i>Congress's motion</i>

04:38.012 --> 04:40.748
<i>to shut her study down.</i>
<i>Let's take a listen.</i>

04:41.749 --> 04:43.316
<i>It is irrefutable.</i>

04:43.651 --> 04:46.486
<i>Our consciousness continues</i>
<i>beyond our physical bodies.</i>

04:46.687 --> 04:48.823
<i>Death is merely a transition</i>

04:48.923 --> 04:50.525
<i>to another existence...</i>

04:50.658 --> 04:52.160
<i>...one we can now see...</i>

04:52.260 --> 04:53.493
<i>...track and record</i>

04:53.594 --> 04:56.329
<i>due to the findings</i>
<i>of my Life Beyond research.</i>

04:57.165 --> 05:00.101
<i>At our institute, we now bridge</i>
<i>dozens of new participants</i>

05:00.367 --> 05:01.636
<i>daily from this world</i>
<i>to the next,</i>

05:01.869 --> 05:04.471
<i>which has led</i>
<i>to astounding breakthroughs.</i>

05:05.338 --> 05:06.641
<i>Soon, we will</i>
<i>be able to comprehend</i>

05:06.874 --> 05:09.076
<i>what was previously</i>
<i>the great unknown.</i>

05:09.710 --> 05:11.546
<i>With countless possibilities</i>
<i>ahead of us,</i>

05:11.746 --> 05:15.183
<i>it is imperative</i>
<i>we continue this research.</i>

05:15.850 --> 05:17.952
<i>Much like many explorers</i>
<i>before us,</i>

05:18.186 --> 05:20.054
<i>we have seen our world expand.</i>

05:20.387 --> 05:23.291
<i>It is now our duty</i>
<i>to discover how far.</i>

05:23.758 --> 05:26.060
<i>Contrary to recent news,</i>
<i>my Life Beyond study,</i>

05:26.294 --> 05:28.029
<i>like all proper</i>
<i>research programs,</i>

05:28.229 --> 05:29.764
<i>is strictly a</i>
<i>volunteer program.</i>

05:30.031 --> 05:34.168
<i>It is a clinical,</i>
<i>not criminal enterprise.</i>

05:34.769 --> 05:37.171
<i>Congress is attempting</i>
<i>to shut us down,</i>

05:37.404 --> 05:38.506
<i>but their efforts only show</i>

05:38.706 --> 05:40.541
<i>how much they fundamentally</i>
<i>misunderstand</i>

05:40.775 --> 05:42.109
<i>the facts of our new reality...</i>

06:18.679 --> 06:21.349
Hey, it's Chad.
I'm here for the TV.

06:21.549 --> 06:22.750
You got the cash?

06:38.733 --> 06:42.069
It works, right?

06:42.402 --> 06:43.537
Yeah.

06:46.540 --> 06:47.875
<i>What do you have to say</i>

06:47.975 --> 06:49.310
<i>about the shootings</i>
<i>taking place?</i>

06:49.577 --> 06:50.945
<i>Everyone needs to calm down.</i>

06:51.045 --> 06:52.513
<i>Congress will sort out</i>
<i>the legislation</i>

06:52.613 --> 06:53.814
<i>- but in the meantime...</i>
- All yours.

06:53.948 --> 06:55.415
<i>...people are adding</i>
<i>to the chaos, all right?</i>

06:55.516 --> 06:57.285
<i>We really need to know more</i>
<i>before any decision.</i>

06:57.518 --> 06:59.020
Hello?

06:59.153 --> 07:00.688
<i>Hello! This is James</i>

07:00.788 --> 07:02.523
<i>from Dr. Stevensen's</i>
<i>Life Beyond study.</i>

07:02.623 --> 07:04.091
<i>Can you please confirm</i>
<i>your password?</i>

07:04.392 --> 07:08.195
Uh. Yeah. It's,
uh, 35 capital FML.

07:09.130 --> 07:10.197
<i>Just checking to confirm,</i>

07:10.398 --> 07:12.233
<i>you declined your flight</i>
<i>to San Francisco</i>

07:12.465 --> 07:14.669
<i>- and requested a car?</i>
- Yeah.

07:14.902 --> 07:16.370
They told me
that would be okay.

07:16.570 --> 07:17.470
<i>Of course.</i>

07:17.805 --> 07:19.407
<i>I'm sending your car rental</i>
<i>information now.</i>

07:19.607 --> 07:21.042
<i>Pick-up is noon today.</i>

07:22.977 --> 07:23.945
I'll be there.

07:24.779 --> 07:26.247
<i>Everything is in order.</i>

07:26.479 --> 07:28.249
<i>Have your confirmation</i>
<i>QR code when you arrive</i>

07:28.448 --> 07:31.886
<i>- and we'll see you soon.</i>
- Okay, thanks. Bye.

07:34.322 --> 07:37.158
So, are you one of those people?

07:37.692 --> 07:41.662
That must be exciting to...
just let it all go.

07:42.263 --> 07:43.564
I respect that.

07:47.568 --> 07:49.870
Can I do anything else
for you before you go?

07:56.310 --> 07:57.878
Let me help you with the TV.

08:03.217 --> 08:04.685
Hey, I can get that.

08:05.419 --> 08:07.254
Hey.

08:09.924 --> 08:10.925
Hey!

08:15.429 --> 08:17.999
Whoa, hey!
Give me back my money!

08:19.633 --> 08:20.701
<i>Just give me the fucking money.</i>

08:22.737 --> 08:24.672
<i>I'm gonna keep</i>
<i>standing out here.</i>

08:26.774 --> 08:27.541
<i>Hello?</i>

08:30.578 --> 08:32.947
<i>You crazy bitch!</i>

08:41.122 --> 08:43.724
No, I got it.
Noon pick-up. I'll be there.

08:44.158 --> 08:45.259
Great. Thank you.

08:46.093 --> 08:47.228
Fuck yeah, Stanley!

08:47.628 --> 08:50.164
Hey, I'm going to San Francisco.

08:50.598 --> 08:51.966
What? You're one of them??

09:01.442 --> 09:02.376
<i>That's right.</i>

09:02.543 --> 09:04.745
<i>We're here live</i>
<i>in San Francisco.</i>

09:05.279 --> 09:06.981
<i>Crowds have gathered</i>
<i>just outside Dr. Stevensen.</i>

09:07.181 --> 09:08.849
I'm just eating breakfast.
Come in. Come in.

09:09.083 --> 09:10.284
<i>The next round...</i>

09:10.384 --> 09:12.119
What the hell's the dog
doing here?

09:14.021 --> 09:15.222
<i>And they're coming out now.</i>

09:15.356 --> 09:17.992
<i>They're taking their positions.</i>
<i>This is very exciting.</i>

09:20.661 --> 09:22.329
<i>Here's Dr. Stevensen herself.</i>

09:22.797 --> 09:24.598
Killing themselves
over this bull bunk.

09:25.166 --> 09:27.334
They say robberies are down
because the robbers

09:27.536 --> 09:29.437
can't get people to do
what they want anymore.

09:29.637 --> 09:31.172
Like dying isn't dying.

09:31.405 --> 09:34.875
Well, it's... it's been proven,
Milton. It's science now.

09:35.276 --> 09:37.745
But science is supposed
to make ya smarter, not dumber.

09:40.381 --> 09:41.849
Hey, look, Milton, um...

09:42.551 --> 09:44.452
I've got to go.
I've got somewhere to be.

09:44.685 --> 09:46.587
What? I put you
on the team for today.

09:46.821 --> 09:48.923
You said you wanted this gig.
You can't do this.

09:49.123 --> 09:52.326
I'm here for Stanley.
I'm... I'm leaving him to you.

09:54.862 --> 09:56.964
<i>We're so</i>
<i>excited to be here to help see</i>

09:57.198 --> 09:59.266
<i>and support</i>
<i>our brave new participants.</i>

09:59.500 --> 10:00.535
<i>Let's give them</i>
<i>a round of applause.</i>

10:00.801 --> 10:03.637
<i>Mm-hmm. Yeah.</i>

10:06.073 --> 10:07.509
It's not the fucking Oscars,
kid.

10:07.608 --> 10:09.076
There's nothing to celebrate.

10:09.610 --> 10:11.112
I'm going to San Francisco.

10:11.612 --> 10:12.480
Teddy...

10:12.680 --> 10:14.181
I'm not asking
for permission.

10:14.448 --> 10:15.749
Teddy, you're...
you're young yet.

10:16.083 --> 10:17.918
You don't know how much
you have to look forward to.

10:18.152 --> 10:20.354
Come on.
We both know that's not true.

10:20.888 --> 10:23.324
I mean, did...
did you see that Niko guy on TV?

10:23.558 --> 10:24.593
I saw a bunch of people.

10:24.825 --> 10:28.662
Every station, every newspaper.
Like him. Like me.

10:29.029 --> 10:32.066
I mean, I'm on that list.
This way...

10:32.700 --> 10:35.769
this way, I... I finally have
a shot at something.

10:37.606 --> 10:39.240
You can't really think that.

10:45.212 --> 10:47.915
You're gonna need some
of this for Stanley, all right?

10:50.184 --> 10:51.352
So this is supposed
to be goodbye?

10:51.586 --> 10:55.856
No. No. I'll... I'll come back
and haunt you.

10:58.092 --> 11:00.661
Okay, listen,
they made me the reservation.

11:00.761 --> 11:02.429
I don't understand why
I have to put a credit card down

11:02.531 --> 11:04.465
- if it's already paid for.
- I'm sorry.

11:04.566 --> 11:06.267
- But it's company policy.
- Right.

11:06.400 --> 11:07.935
If you'd like,
I will call corporate

11:08.035 --> 11:09.370
- and triple-check.
- Please. Do it.

11:09.470 --> 11:10.971
Hello!
I can help you over here, sir.

11:11.105 --> 11:12.373
Hey. Uh, yeah.
I have a car reserved for me

11:12.406 --> 11:13.941
- for a noon pick-up.
- Great.

11:13.974 --> 11:15.577
I just need your credit card
and driver's license.

11:15.644 --> 11:18.513
Yeah. Ah... Here you go.

11:18.712 --> 11:19.847
Perfect. Thank you.

11:19.947 --> 11:21.849
Oh, I'm sorry, sir.
This expires in a week.

11:21.949 --> 11:23.250
I won't be needing
it past then.

11:23.350 --> 11:24.985
You'll need
a valid driver's license

11:25.085 --> 11:27.154
that doesn't expire for two
months in order to rent a car.

11:27.254 --> 11:29.524
That makes no sense.
It's valid for when I need it.

11:29.790 --> 11:31.458
Just so you know, Blossom...

11:31.560 --> 11:32.459
Rose.

11:32.594 --> 11:33.727
...you have to have
a credit card

11:33.827 --> 11:35.429
if you want us
to rent you a car.

11:35.597 --> 11:37.364
This is insane.
This is literally insane.

11:37.464 --> 11:38.933
They made me the reservation.

11:39.166 --> 11:42.036
- Just one second.
- Thanks.

11:45.773 --> 11:48.075
All right?

11:48.677 --> 11:50.311
Are you two together?

11:50.477 --> 11:51.513
- Hey.
- Excuse me?

11:51.680 --> 11:52.780
She should be
so lucky.

11:53.047 --> 11:56.585
It seems the same company
has reserved both your cars.

11:56.685 --> 11:58.352
And they both have
the same destination.

11:59.688 --> 12:00.721
When's your appointment?

12:01.121 --> 12:03.991
- Um, seven days.
- Mine's in five.

12:04.291 --> 12:05.259
You a serial killer?

12:05.726 --> 12:07.895
Yeah, no. No, I say.
No, definitely not.

12:08.095 --> 12:09.664
No. Promise.
Never killed anyone.

12:09.897 --> 12:10.798
Shame.

12:11.198 --> 12:12.466
Well, maybe
we could help each other.

12:12.567 --> 12:13.635
In killing each other?

12:13.734 --> 12:16.804
Well, uh, no.
Getting to Dr. Stevensen's.

12:17.071 --> 12:19.406
- You're British, huh?
- Innit.

12:22.309 --> 12:23.477
Do you have earbuds?

12:26.013 --> 12:27.047
Awesome. So you, uh,

12:27.481 --> 12:29.316
you want to take the first shift
and then we'll do a swap out?

12:29.416 --> 12:32.152
- You can't drive.
- That's not true.

12:32.353 --> 12:33.787
I can turn the wheel
and everything.

12:33.887 --> 12:35.523
Can even stay
on the right side of the road.

12:35.624 --> 12:36.991
Or is it the left?

12:37.424 --> 12:38.259
I'm just kidding.

12:38.526 --> 12:41.095
We just need to get away
from these rental fuckers.

12:44.265 --> 12:45.199
Finally!

12:47.301 --> 12:48.102
An adventure, right?

12:48.335 --> 12:49.903
You know
what's at the end of this.

12:50.237 --> 12:52.106
Yeah, everything
I've ever wanted.

12:52.641 --> 12:53.774
You?

12:54.275 --> 12:55.142
It's Blossom, right?

12:55.543 --> 12:57.044
- Rose.
- Ah.

12:58.747 --> 13:00.281
I go by my middle name.

13:01.382 --> 13:03.484
Sweet.
So you prefer Rose or Rosie?

13:03.784 --> 13:04.785
Rose.

13:05.319 --> 13:06.655
By the way, uh, I'm Teddy.

13:08.188 --> 13:10.424
- That's a pretty name.
- I'm not interested.

13:10.791 --> 13:12.126
Excuse me?
I wasn't offering.

13:12.326 --> 13:13.794
Can you, uh,
crack your window, please?

13:14.028 --> 13:16.598
- It smells like smoke in here.
- Oh, that's actually not me.

13:16.797 --> 13:19.800
Um, I, uh, I... I don't smoke.

13:20.000 --> 13:22.604
Well, uh, I work with
some guys who do, and...

13:23.003 --> 13:25.272
Yeah, when they're not
lifting stuff, they, uh...

13:26.273 --> 13:27.174
they just light up.

13:27.542 --> 13:30.177
So, and I don't see the point
in doing laundry anymore, so.

13:30.377 --> 13:32.714
Oh. Please don't, uh.

13:32.980 --> 13:34.982
- Ah.
- Seventeen missed calls.

13:40.387 --> 13:41.690
<i>Oh, and thanks for the license.</i>

13:42.022 --> 13:45.259
<i>Yeah, I, uh, can't be arsed</i>
<i>with that paperwork shit, so.</i>

13:46.327 --> 13:47.428
<i>Yeah. Um...</i>

13:48.530 --> 13:50.230
<i>so, what do you do?</i>

13:50.497 --> 13:52.166
<i>Did? What... What did you do?</i>

13:52.399 --> 13:55.436
<i>Um, what did you do?</i>
<i>You're a mover?</i>

13:55.570 --> 13:57.304
<i>I actually, uh,</i>
<i>I used to have my own company.</i>

13:57.404 --> 14:00.474
<i>Had a few, actually.</i>
<i>And, uh, you know...</i>

14:00.709 --> 14:01.643
<i>Mm-hmm.</i>

14:01.975 --> 14:03.077
<i>Sometimes you need</i>
<i>the extra cash, right?</i>

14:03.344 --> 14:04.912
<i>Do you want</i>
<i>to put those earbuds on?</i>

14:05.145 --> 14:06.815
<i>Maybe you can</i>
<i>use the Bluetooth.</i>

14:07.014 --> 14:09.718
<i>Hey, look,</i>
<i>there's an article about us.</i>

14:10.117 --> 14:14.589
<i>Human Rights Activist</i>
<i>Maya Cam. Camp-yon.</i>

14:14.823 --> 14:15.824
<i>- Cam... Camp-yon.</i>
<i>- Campion.</i>

14:16.190 --> 14:18.258
<i>Camp-yon... Campion</i>
<i>issued a formal statement</i>

14:18.459 --> 14:21.395
<i>declaring that the right</i>
<i>to die is a civil liberty.</i>

14:22.564 --> 14:23.565
<i>Damn straight.</i>

14:23.964 --> 14:25.399
<i>And who the fuck</i>
<i>are these senators</i>

14:25.600 --> 14:26.601
<i>who are trying to control us?</i>

14:27.736 --> 14:30.170
<i>People who don't believe,</i>
<i>or don't want to believe.</i>

15:14.783 --> 15:16.016
I got you chips.

15:20.522 --> 15:22.022
How can you eat that shit?

15:22.791 --> 15:24.291
What? Is there a better time?

15:25.660 --> 15:27.562
I wonder if cows
get to be ghosts.

15:27.995 --> 15:29.898
- Definitely not.
- How do you know?

15:30.197 --> 15:32.466
Because there'd be
a whole bunch of mad angry cows

15:32.667 --> 15:33.768
haunting the shit outta me.

15:34.001 --> 15:36.069
Ah. Hopefully pigs make the cut.

15:37.839 --> 15:39.406
Oh, it's an insult. I'm the pig.

15:39.541 --> 15:41.141
- It's just a thought.
- Hmm. Hmm.

15:41.241 --> 15:42.644
Just a thought.

15:42.744 --> 15:44.411
Any other thoughts?

15:44.579 --> 15:45.946
<i>Things have changed.</i>

15:46.213 --> 15:49.517
<i>If you have something left</i>
<i>to say to someone who's passed,</i>

15:49.884 --> 15:51.051
<i>we are here for you.</i>

15:51.519 --> 15:53.788
<i>Our three mediums</i>
<i>are standing by...</i>

15:53.888 --> 15:55.055
Hey, someone
really wants to chat.

15:55.155 --> 15:56.156
<i>...deliver your</i>
<i>messages to your</i>

15:56.190 --> 15:57.191
<i>loved ones on the other side.</i>

15:57.257 --> 15:58.992
Ah. The mystery
continues, eh?

15:59.226 --> 16:01.361
<i>- Retrial.</i>
<i>- Where are those earbuds?</i>

16:01.563 --> 16:02.564
I haven't seen them yet.

16:04.699 --> 16:08.368
- Willing driver.
- With no valid license.

16:08.636 --> 16:11.104
- Only on a technicality.
- I'm not taking any risks.

16:11.305 --> 16:12.674
Oh, right, yeah. Me driving.

16:12.774 --> 16:14.241
That's the biggest risk
right now.

16:16.410 --> 16:19.146
Did I tell you I also know
how to use the blinkers?

16:32.259 --> 16:34.428
- King or queen for you folks?
- Two rooms, please.

16:34.629 --> 16:38.098
- The further apart, the better.
- We're trying to conceive.

16:39.901 --> 16:43.671
- Two rooms that we do have...
- Whatever two rooms you have.

16:46.173 --> 16:48.442
Oh, um, if you find me
dead in the morning,

16:48.643 --> 16:51.278
she did it. Yeah.
Be sure to thank her for me.

16:59.954 --> 17:01.088
Oh.

17:04.592 --> 17:06.861
- 6:00 a.m., you got it?
- Just so I know,

17:06.961 --> 17:08.328
is it gonna be like this
the whole trip?

17:08.863 --> 17:11.398
I need to be in San Francisco
in four days for my appointment.

17:11.599 --> 17:14.002
That requires us
not fucking around. Okay?

17:14.334 --> 17:15.837
Anyway, that's not
what I'm talking about.

17:15.970 --> 17:16.971
What are you
talking about?

17:17.337 --> 17:19.574
You don't have to be
an asshole the whole time.

17:20.542 --> 17:22.209
Excuse me?

17:23.410 --> 17:24.177
You heard.

17:24.378 --> 17:26.113
Let me make something
really clear to you.

17:26.346 --> 17:27.916
We're not buddies.
We're not pals.

17:28.115 --> 17:30.384
We're not
in this together. Okay?

17:30.752 --> 17:31.485
Bollocks.

17:31.953 --> 17:34.087
How many people know what
it's like to be us right now?

17:35.657 --> 17:38.492
6:00 a.m., the car leaves.
Be in it or don't.

17:39.493 --> 17:40.795
- Sharp.
- Razor.

17:43.665 --> 17:47.367
Oh, my God! Stop following me.
I don't want to be your friend!

17:49.804 --> 17:50.738
What?

18:28.543 --> 18:30.210
<i>Rose.</i>

18:54.736 --> 18:56.470
<i>On the sector from Wall Street,</i>

18:56.571 --> 18:58.305
<i>the blue chips fell victim</i>
<i>to a sell-off...</i>

19:21.261 --> 19:22.396
<i>They are so easy...</i>

19:22.630 --> 19:24.132
<i>...at</i>
<i>the first pitch and fouled it</i>

19:24.231 --> 19:26.400
<i>deep back</i>
<i>into the stands behind...</i>

19:31.204 --> 19:32.707
<i>Hi, is this the front desk?</i>

19:33.206 --> 19:35.242
Is there anything good
to do around here?

19:35.510 --> 19:37.679
<i>Hey there,</i>
<i>I don't want this in my house.</i>

19:39.747 --> 19:41.149
<i>Sorry, but my grandmother...</i>

19:41.381 --> 19:43.051
<i>...why</i>
<i>this study is so important.</i>

19:43.250 --> 19:45.086
<i>So let's get to the question</i>

19:45.318 --> 19:47.254
<i>that's on</i>
<i>everyone's mind, I think.</i>

19:47.889 --> 19:51.092
<i>Are you asking people</i>
<i>to end their lives?</i>

19:52.060 --> 19:54.629
