No. Nothing was wrong
with me back then.

1:06:49.176 --> 1:06:52.212
I was perfect.

1:06:52.680 --> 1:06:54.782
You know, I spent so long...

1:06:56.016 --> 1:06:58.485
trying to show you
that I was better than you.

1:06:59.286 --> 1:07:02.524
