1:07:58.980 --> 1:07:59.981
I'm sorry.

1:08:00.080 --> 1:08:02.550
Hmm. It's okay.
I didn't know him.

1:08:03.017 --> 1:08:04.284
We didn't need him.

1:08:05.118 --> 1:08:07.220
