1:08:54.035 --> 1:08:55.937
I was just so ashamed and...

1:08:56.871 --> 1:09:01.408
scared that they'd judge me
so I didn't pick up their calls.

1:09:02.877 --> 1:09:05.178
I was so stupid. I...

1:09:14.555 --> 1:09:15.657
Do you see her?

1:09:19.459 --> 1:09:21.328
I just want
to make things right.

1:09:24.398 --> 1:09:26.400
