a self-destruct button

1:11:06.801 --> 1:11:07.902
in my heart...

1:11:09.269 --> 1:11:11.471
and it's fucking irresistible.

1:11:15.475 --> 1:11:16.944
Oh, I can be happy...

1:11:18.746 --> 1:11:19.847
for a minute,

1:11:20.581 --> 1:11:22.049
a day, maybe even a year...

1:11:24.685 --> 1:11:27.021
but sooner or later,
I'm pushing that button.

1:11:32.459 --> 1:11:34.629
You never spoke
to your sister after that?

1:11:37.231 --> 1:11:38.331
No.

1:11:41.602 --> 1:11:43.838
I kept waiting for that call.

1:11:45.106 --> 1:11:47.307
But no, her calls are concerned.

1:11:49.911 --> 1:11:51.579
And that's worse somehow.

1:11:58.318 --> 1:12:00.655
I just don't want
to hurt anymore.

1:12:22.243 --> 1:12:23.376
Hey.

1:12:23.611 --> 1:12:27.815
Um, look, I, uh,
I need to say something to you.

1:12:28.049 --> 1:12:29.717
I don't want to talk
about that stuff anymore.

1:12:29.917 --> 1:12:32.119
No. No, no, no. I need
to tell you something else.

1:12:32.452 --> 1:12:34.387
I don't wanna talk
about that stuff either.

1:13:14.662 --> 1:13:15.663
<i>Hello?</i>

1:13:16.030 --> 1:13:18.866
Milton...
...you handsome bastard.

1:13:19.367 --> 1:13:20.968
<i>I knew I'd hear from you.</i>

1:13:21.669 --> 1:13:23.704
Yeah, we're just
on our way to Arizona now.

1:13:24.205 --> 1:13:25.539
<i>Are you coming home?</i>

1:13:27.241 --> 1:13:28.809
<i>Ah. Um,</i>

1:13:29.442 --> 1:13:30.645
<i>I've met someone.</i>

1:13:31.345 --> 1:13:33.147
<i>That's fantastic.</i>

1:13:33.681 --> 1:13:35.816
<i>But I think</i>
<i>you'd really like her. She's...</i>

1:13:36.984 --> 1:13:37.985
<i>She's smart.</i>

1:13:39.153 --> 1:13:39.820
Real.

1:13:40.288 --> 1:13:43.190
<i>That's wonderful. I told you.</i>
<i>You just never know.</i>

1:13:46.294 --> 1:13:48.029
<i>So are you two coming back?</i>

1:13:50.631 --> 1:13:52.366
<i>Will I get to meet this girl?</i>

1:13:52.465 --> 1:13:53.634
Hey, um, no. I've gotta go.

1:13:53.801 --> 1:13:54.936
- Can you, uh, kiss...
- <i>Teddy!</i>

1:13:55.002 --> 1:13:57.470
- ...Stanley for me, okay?
<i>- Teddy.</i>

1:13:59.740 --> 1:14:01.509
- That's a choice.
- I feel like it's fitting.

1:14:01.742 --> 1:14:04.078
Yeah. Oh, I'm glad.
Yeah, that's...

1:14:04.312 --> 1:14:05.713
Oh, I've got one too. Fantastic.

1:14:05.947 --> 1:14:06.681
- Twins.
- Yeah.

1:14:06.814 --> 1:14:07.748
It's just what
I wanted actually.

1:14:08.082 --> 1:14:09.550
Yeah. I was gonna ask you
when you were going in

1:14:09.684 --> 1:14:10.885
could you grab me
a pair of these?

1:14:10.952 --> 1:14:12.320
- Looks great on you.
- Perfect.

1:14:12.420 --> 1:14:13.654
<i>Yeah.</i>

1:14:35.009 --> 1:14:38.145
Hey. Teddy, we're here.

1:14:49.590 --> 1:14:50.825
What?

1:14:51.058 --> 1:14:52.093
Rose!

1:14:52.526 --> 1:14:54.462
Rose!

1:14:54.729 --> 1:14:56.931
Hey!

1:14:57.465 --> 1:14:59.166
