1:15:32.767 --> 1:15:34.635
Oh, uh, can I get you guys
something to drink?

1:15:34.869 --> 1:15:37.204
- A coffee maybe?
- Hi, kiddo.

1:15:37.605 --> 1:15:38.939
Oh, look at that.

1:15:39.106 --> 1:15:39.807
Look at that.

1:15:40.041 --> 1:15:41.642
Um, maybe a glass of wine
would be good.

1:15:41.742 --> 1:15:43.277
You have to see my room,
we changed it!

1:15:43.377 --> 1:15:44.645
- You have to see!
- Okay.

1:15:44.779 --> 1:15:47.748
Bring her back. Mommy wants
to see her, too.

1:15:48.115 --> 1:15:49.050
Whoo!

1:15:54.822 --> 1:15:56.490
You know, I forgot my manners.

1:15:56.690 --> 1:15:58.059
- Heather. Hi.
- Oh. Teddy.

1:15:58.159 --> 1:15:58.926
- Teddy?
- Yes.

1:15:59.126 --> 1:16:00.561
Sounds like
there's a story. Come inside.

1:16:00.661 --> 1:16:02.229
Nick.

1:16:02.496 --> 1:16:03.798
Okay.

1:16:22.083 --> 1:16:22.950
Hmm.

