1:17:12.266 --> 1:17:14.502
Well, no, no.
I've got stuff to do tonight.

1:17:14.603 --> 1:17:15.970
And I don't...
I don't feel well.

1:17:16.170 --> 1:17:17.338
Yeah, well, suck it up.

1:17:18.939 --> 1:17:21.775
Big baby.

1:17:21.976 --> 1:17:23.677
- Such a baby.
- Oh.

1:17:23.878 --> 1:17:25.446
God, this is a story.

1:17:25.679 --> 1:17:26.947
Yeah, well,

1:17:27.047 --> 1:17:28.883
it's a doozy
of a story how we met, huh?

1:17:28.983 --> 1:17:30.519
I don't know that
I could tell that right.

1:17:30.619 --> 1:17:31.652
No, you can't so...

1:17:31.785 --> 1:17:33.988
No, no. I can. I can.
I can tell it right.

1:17:34.088 --> 1:17:35.923
Um, so the...

1:17:37.658 --> 1:17:39.860
