1:18:14.728 --> 1:18:18.032
What? That's...
That's amazing.

1:18:18.533 --> 1:18:19.400
When?

1:18:19.668 --> 1:18:22.903
Uh. We're going
to Vegas tonight.

1:18:23.103 --> 1:18:24.772
Gonna do a drive-through
wedding thing.

1:18:25.005 --> 1:18:26.508
Oh, my God, that's insane.

1:18:26.641 --> 1:18:29.009
Yeah. We're selling the car.

1:18:29.310 --> 1:18:31.345
And, uh, then
we're gonna go to Europe.

1:18:31.613 --> 1:18:33.047
