1:19:11.785 --> 1:19:13.354
And I'm... I'm just gonna...

1:19:13.854 --> 1:19:15.690
...look for a teaching job.

1:19:16.223 --> 1:19:19.226
And Teddy's got this
brilliant idea for a startup,

1:19:19.793 --> 1:19:21.428
so he's gonna get
that going there.

1:19:22.096 --> 1:19:23.063
And, um...

1:19:24.064 --> 1:19:26.200
we've been making these lists.

1:19:26.601 --> 1:19:29.470
Um, things we've always
wanted to do.

1:19:30.004 --> 1:19:31.372
We've been doing that together.

1:19:32.172 --> 1:19:34.908
For some reason, we've never
let ourselves do that before.

1:19:39.146 --> 1:19:40.047
That's it.

1:19:40.814 --> 1:19:43.551
That's why I wanted to see you.

1:19:44.753 --> 1:19:45.754
Both.

1:19:46.387 --> 1:19:49.290
I'm so happy for you.
It's crazy.

1:19:49.490 --> 1:19:52.960
It's not... not bad crazy.
It's just... it's amazing.

1:19:53.327 --> 1:19:54.895
Yeah.

1:19:55.530 --> 1:19:56.497
Mm-hmm.

1:20:07.709 --> 1:20:08.876
Well, you, uh,

1:20:09.076 --> 1:20:10.477
