1:20:13.447 --> 1:20:14.549
It's nice to meet you, man.

1:20:15.717 --> 1:20:16.950
Hey, Ladybug.

1:20:22.022 --> 1:20:24.124
I just wanted to say, um...

1:20:29.863 --> 1:20:32.066
