and it doesn't help.

1:21:00.928 --> 1:21:02.229
I don't need you
to fix my problems.

1:21:02.363 --> 1:21:04.431
I just want you
to take care of your own.

1:21:07.569 --> 1:21:08.435
Honey, we...

1:21:09.303 --> 1:21:11.038
- we gotta get dinner for Steph.
- Oh,

1:21:11.238 --> 1:21:13.340
of course. Yes.
