1:25:53.153 --> 1:25:54.154
to do this now.

1:25:54.354 --> 1:25:55.455
Well, uh,

1:25:55.690 --> 1:25:57.357
Dr. Stevensen
flew in just for it,

1:25:57.457 --> 1:25:58.826
- but...
