1:26:00.928 --> 1:26:01.896
Nurse Ala?

1:26:02.262 --> 1:26:05.332
Mm-hmm?
- Uh. Just one second.

1:26:06.134 --> 1:26:11.839
Um.

1:26:13.641 --> 1:26:16.209
Okay,
so let's see what we can do. Um,

1:26:16.511 --> 1:26:17.612
we'll start your paperwork

1:26:17.912 --> 1:26:20.982
and there's a video for you
to watch before your journey

1:26:21.415 --> 1:26:23.951
so we can get you started
there in a few minutes.

1:26:24.052 --> 1:26:25.452
- Does that sound good?
- Yeah.

1:26:26.154 --> 1:26:28.188
Okay. Follow me.

1:26:30.892 --> 1:26:32.192
And, uh, you, sir.

1:26:32.426 --> 1:26:34.762
Will you be coming back
for your appointment or...

1:26:43.571 --> 1:26:45.472
I thought this was
what you wanted.

1:26:46.607 --> 1:26:47.608
Not anymore.

1:26:50.377 --> 1:26:52.947
Okay, so
we are ready for you upstairs.

1:26:55.016 --> 1:26:58.553
Um, would you like
to watch the video together?

1:27:04.559 --> 1:27:05.960
<i>Congratulations!</i>

1:27:06.226 --> 1:27:07.394
<i>You are on your way to being</i>

1:27:07.528 --> 1:27:09.797
<i>an imperative part</i>
<i>of our Life Beyond study.</i>

1:27:10.430 --> 1:27:11.465
<i>You are ready to step</i>

1:27:11.699 --> 1:27:14.001
<i>into the next stage</i>
<i>of evolution with us.</i>

1:27:14.468 --> 1:27:17.939
<i>You are a pioneer</i>
<i>who will forever be remembered</i>

1:27:18.172 --> 1:27:19.907
<i>for your bravery</i>
<i>in building branches</i>

1:27:20.108 --> 1:27:22.510
<i>between this world</i>
<i>and the next.</i>

1:27:26.848 --> 1:27:27.849
Is that it?

1:27:32.419 --> 1:27:34.589
Okay, we are all set up

1:27:34.689 --> 1:27:36.389
to track and record
your journey.

1:27:36.657 --> 1:27:39.259
I'll be there the whole time
to help you transition smoothly.

1:27:39.493 --> 1:27:42.530
- Um, do you have any questions?
- Will it hurt?

1:27:42.864 --> 1:27:44.832
The IV can
be a little uncomfortable

1:27:44.966 --> 1:27:46.333
but we can numb the spot first.

1:27:46.534 --> 1:27:48.536
We begin with a sedative
to help you relax.

1:27:48.736 --> 1:27:50.470
It's a lot like
going under for surgery.

1:27:50.705 --> 1:27:52.206
Once you're in
a state of passing

1:27:52.439 --> 1:27:55.109
and we can see that you've
crossed on our tracking devices,

1:27:55.342 --> 1:27:57.578
then we terminate
your physical form.

1:27:58.345 --> 1:27:59.847
None of that will hurt.

1:28:02.315 --> 1:28:03.483
Are you ready?

1:28:06.554 --> 1:28:08.022
Yeah. Let's just do it. Yeah.

1:28:08.222 --> 1:28:09.957
Absolutely.
So you can follow me

1:28:10.191 --> 1:28:13.628
and we'll get you changed
and started in the Passing Room.

1:28:14.327 --> 1:28:16.463
Mm-hmm.

1:28:21.235 --> 1:28:23.738
Sir, do you want to step
into the waiting room?

1:28:24.005 --> 1:28:25.072
Can I stay?

1:28:27.041 --> 1:28:28.709
It is important
that you have a calm

1:28:28.910 --> 1:28:31.846
- and positive experience...
- He can stay.

1:28:32.547 --> 1:28:35.683
Okay. Yeah. It's good.
Come on in.

1:28:44.125 --> 1:28:45.293
Okay.

