Okay. Here comes the needle.

1:29:19.093 --> 1:29:20.761
- Are you ready?
- Mm-hmm.

1:29:21.229 --> 1:29:23.496
In three, two, one.

1:29:24.464 --> 1:29:25.766
Is that okay?

1:29:43.284 --> 1:29:44.652
Okay.
That feel comfortable?

1:29:44.752 --> 1:29:45.653
Yes.

1:29:49.757 --> 1:29:50.658
All right.

1:29:52.093 --> 1:29:53.393
Shall we?

1:30:00.768 --> 1:30:01.669
Okay.

1:30:04.639 --> 1:30:06.240
- No. Just one...
- Sir!

