- No. Sir. Sir.
- Just give me...

1:30:07.675 --> 1:30:09.409
Hey, hey, hey.
Just give me one more day.

1:30:09.510 --> 1:30:11.178
- Sir.
- Teddy, what does it matter?

1:30:11.312 --> 1:30:12.346
One hour.
Just give me that.

1:30:12.580 --> 1:30:13.581
What if I can't?

1:30:13.814 --> 1:30:15.883
Ten... Ten minutes
to think about how you can.

1:30:16.083 --> 1:30:16.884
I don't deserve it.

1:30:17.018 --> 1:30:19.620
Five minutes
to you realize that you do.

1:30:21.289 --> 1:30:22.422
No, one minute.

1:30:22.790 --> 1:30:25.760
One minute to think
about what you did yesterday.

1:30:26.794 --> 1:30:28.396
Not... Not what happened
in the past,

1:30:28.663 --> 1:30:30.097
not what happened
when you were younger...

1:30:30.831 --> 1:30:32.199
and not the things
you can't control

1:30:32.400 --> 1:30:33.466
or the mistakes you made.

1:30:33.668 --> 1:30:36.370
Please. Just...
...one minute.

1:30:36.737 --> 1:30:39.707
Just give me one more minute.

1:30:41.309 --> 1:30:42.576
Wait.

1:30:47.480 --> 1:30:48.816
Rose.

1:31:39.834 --> 1:31:41.902
Mom?

1:31:43.938 --> 1:31:45.506
I'm sorry.

1:31:46.707 --> 1:31:50.111
I'm sorry.
I'm sorry I wasn't there.

1:31:50.344 --> 1:31:54.682
I tried. I tried hard.
I couldn't. I... I...

