1:36:13.307 --> 1:36:14.475
<i>I'm here.</i>

1:37:24.912 --> 1:37:27.181
<i>You can do it. Come on.</i>

1:37:37.124 --> 1:37:43.330
Just... Just
give me one minute, please.

